profile:
Centennial Windows & Doors is a family owned and operated business that offers an end-to-end solution for replacement windows and doors. We sell, manufacture, install, and service our own complete line of award winning, energy efficient windows and doors.
 
Why homeowners choose Centennial Windows & Doors
 
The Best Warranty
- We provide a 100% warranty on everything we do for as long as you own your home – NO fine print and NO exclusions. And if you sell your home, it's transferable to new homeowners within 10 years of purchasing Centennial windows and doors.
 
Responsibility and Accountability
- We take full responsibility to manufacture, install, and service your windows and doors. You are dealing with ONE company only and one phone number. 
 
Proven Installation Quality
- We DO NOT hire subcontractors. All work is performed by our full time, uniformed employees, fully covered under Workers’ Compensation. Centennial Installers were the first in Canada to write the Canadian Standards Association (CSA) Fenestration Installation Technician (FIT) certification exam.
 
Leaders in Energy Efficiency
- Centennial Windows & Doors was the first window company in Canada to be ENERGY STAR® certified. We have been awarded the:
          - 2004 – ENERGY STAR Manufacturer of the Year Award
          - 2005 – ENERGY STAR Retailer of the Year Award
          - 2008 – ENERGY STAR Sustained Excellence Award
          - 2014 – ENERGY STAR Manufacturer of the Year Award – Windows and Doors
- Since 2013, our windows have been recognized as ENERGY STAR Most Efficient.

profile:
Diamond Home Improvement was established in 1983 by the Gillen Family. Perseverance, determination and hard work have made Diamond Home Improvement an industry leader in Windsor and Essex County. Our commitment to 100% customer satisfaction is evident throughout all levels of our organization. With Diamond, our customers are guaranteed a professional, courteous experience from their initial phone call to the completion of their project.

Our knowledgeable staff is ready to answer you calls and our 24 hour answering service ensures the level of customer care we offer at Diamond Home Improvement. The friendly sales staff is always prepared to provide you with innovative ideas for your project. They will spend the time with you to make your project what you envision. Our 100% customer satisfaction is what creates “customers for life”.

Our professional installation teams are what make your dreams into reality, offering only the highest quality in workmanship. Our entire team will supervise your project from start to finish.

Since 1983 we have been a leader in the roofing industry in Windsor and Essex County. Our trained sales staff will provide you with a detailed evaluation of your roof project in the comfort of your own home. Our professional installation teams will ensure your complete satisfaction from beginning to end. We are insurance claim specialists and can also provide you with the best warranties in the business. Our new lifetime warranty shingle will provide you with the last roof you will ever need!

We are the local authorized dealer for Lifestyle Sunrooms. Lifestyle is Canada’s largest sunroom manufacturer. The Oasis Series will allow you and your family to enjoy the outdoors from inside the comfort of your own home. We offer three different lines of sunrooms: The Oasis, The Oasis Plus and the Grand Oasis. We will custom design your sunroom, uniquely to fit your home. Our trained installers will guarantee your complete approval from start to finish. Open your imagination and create your own backyard oasis!

Diamond Home Improvement is also the authorized dealer for Lifestyle Windows. Lifestyle Windows have achieved the highest energy star rating available. We have a variety of styles and colors to compliment your home. Our friendly sales staff will provide a thorough evaluation and estimate for your new windows. Our factory-trained installers will ensure your new windows will provide you many years of warmth and comfort!

profile:
DuraVu Windows & Doors offers a wide selection of quality custom window, patio and entry door styles, designs and colours to meet your specific needs and budget. Designed for beauty and engineered for strength and durability, our custom vinyl windows and custom steel and fiberglass doors meet or exceed Energy Star qualifications and are manufactured to the highest CSA standards. 


The DuraVu Difference. We’ve brought together an experienced team into a new kind of company to create a fresh and positive experience for our customers. We founded this company because we wanted to create a better window and door experience for our customers. We simply want to do things better based on four very simple principles:
- Treat everyone with dignity and respect
- Always work hard and never stop learning
- Always do the right thing 
- Never compromise on quality


Windows and Doors from a Clearer Point of View. There are plenty of window and door companies to choose from. And plenty that claim to provide the best quality products, price, service and installation. At DuraVu (pronounced, Dur-a-view), you won’t hear a lot of hype talk, because we’d rather spend time showing our customers the DuraVu difference by educating them, fully explaining what to look for in choosing the right replacement windows and doors for their home. 


At DuraVu, we are motivated by a mission to improve the comfort, beauty and value of your home. From features and technology to energy ratings and proper installation, we want you to understand the benefits of what we have to offer and why we do things the way we do. No matter the size or budget of the project, we pride ourselves on providing a courteous, honest and individualized approach to each and every customer. Let us help you make the right choice for your home with our professional in-home showroom experience. Our representatives are consultants who will help you make an informed decision that meets your needs and preferences. We look forward to showing you a clearer point of view so you can make a truly informed and confident decision that lasts a lifetime. 


Quality Assured - Partnerships and Certifications:
DuraVu Windows & Doors Inc. is proud to partner with the Vinyl Window Design Group (VWD), a premier Canadian manufacturer of leading quality windows and doors. Known for leading-edge design innovation, manufacturing excellence and technology, VWD has been certified and recognized for its quality manufacturing, quality and energy efficient products.
- CSA approved and inspected
- National Fenestration Rating Council approved
- Window Wise approved manufacturer
- Energy Star certified Windows and Doors
- 2006-2016 Energy Star Dealers’ Choice 
- 2015 Energy Star Promoter of the Year, Energy Star Most Efficient
- 2014 Energy Star Sustained Excellence
- 2012 Energy Star Advocate of the Year, Windows, Doors & Skylights
- 2006 Energy Star Manufacturer of the Year, Windows, Doors and Skylights
